title.rendered: BUSHWAKKA – THE EXTREME DARKNESS ENDO – LHS (PASSENGER SIDE)

content.rendered:
Introducing the BUSHWAKKA – THE EXTREME DARKNESS ENDO – LHS (PASSENGER SIDE) 270+

Talk about upgrades and Changing the Game…

 

2300 long x 180 high x 140 Wide and only 28kg

The New Extreme Darkness carries a well developed ENDO frame and upgraded hinge design

The built in LED lights is a new feature that we introduce.

600 D rip stop Polyester Canvas

Aluminium Square Tube Framing

Black ENDO frame

Black Arms

1 x built in leg – moveable to other arms

2 x Rope Ratchet

2 x Standard L Brackets – requires rust treatment if located close to the shore.

304 Stainless Steel bolts – requires rust treatment if located close to the shore.

 

Please note due to the size of this item it is pick up only from our store in Coffs Harbour. 

 

To see the full range of Bushwakka adventure gear available at Automax 4X4 click here.

Be sure to follow us on Facebook and Instagram to get your 4WD fix.
